Running command: cat > check_solution.py << 'PY'
from solution import Solution

cases = [
    (5,7),
    (10,15),
    (3,3),
    (1,1),
    (2,3),
    (4,7),
    (7,7),
    (8,15),
    (15,15),
    (16,31),
    (31,31),
    (32,63),
]

s = Solution()
all_ok = True
for n, expected in cases:
    out = s.smallestNumber(n)
    ok = out == expected
    print(n, out, expected, 'OK' if ok else 'FAIL')
    if not ok:
        all_ok = False

print('ALL OK' if all_ok else 'SOME FAIL')
